{"tid":1656061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《仲差好多，每人捐少少》JASON(大J) 眾籌幫助日本受台風侵襲後重建","createTime":"2019-10-15T11:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T00:56:27.000Z","uid":163734,"like":44,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"7d00bc0bcec899aebf15c8632173aa1b7b45e927","tid":1656061,"uid":163734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:33:05.000Z","msg":"JASON(大J) 眾籌幫助日本受台風侵襲後重建<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n眾籌連結：<a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/y3sewzmg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fy3sewzmg&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLLP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=24cfef24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/y3sewzmg</a><br />\n<br />\n每人捐少少好快達標<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n$10、$20、$50、$100、$200 都好呀！<br />\n唔洗多，出去食少一餐都喺返度啦～<br />\n國際戰線！同眾籌幫手足都可以同步進行！<br />\n真心希望大家每人捐少少。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nJASON(大J)  YouTube 解釋今次眾籌嘅意義！多多益善，小小無拘！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y6DhMC3q5MI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY6DhMC3q5MI&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLLP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=96c61434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y6DhMC3q5MI</a>"},{"pid":"c3321fd1cfe71c37ef37973954aec32574d14638","tid":1656061,"uid":163734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:33:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c67ff8d214be180bc8635e801e01ddc049ad962","tid":1656061,"uid":163734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7252f07e4dce93ce30f390323ac4aa76f5b09e6c","tid":1656061,"uid":163734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T11:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8